preinstall:
have python
have ruby
ideally don't be running any other python

run:
pull everything into an empty directory
create the following files
creds: your login username (a@b.c)
target: zendesk URL
token: API token
run bash quickinit
run ./startserver
go to 127.0.0.1:65000 in a browser

for next release:

breached tickets are displayed in solid red (done)
add a button in the UI that calls ./DOAPITOUCHES
have a config file that maps customer tier to a color, and have certain customers of that tier be displayed in that color
